description:
BOOKINGS ONLY.  
We are a drive thru Vaccination Centre during Levels 3 and 4 on Te Whiti Park. Please note our Thursday late night will now close at 4.00pm.
Children aged 12-15years are able to have their vaccination if their parents/caregivers have an existing booking at our centre on the day. 

You will need to wait and be observed in your vehicle for 15 minutes after your vaccination.
You must wear a facemask and be prepared to expose your full shoulder and upper arm without removing your facemask.

If you are a Walk-In with an existing booking, please ensure you are dressed warm enough for the weather as there may be a queue outside and keep 2meters distance from others.

DO NOT ATTEND and PLEASE REBOOK If you are... 
Unwell with cold or flu like symptoms, have a sore throat, a cough, a high fever etc.  You have been to any locations of interest, are awaiting a COVID test or have been asked to stay home and self isolate.
